'''Douglas Thomas Washton''' (March 16, 1995 - May 14, 2053), dubbed the "'''Classmate Clubber'''," was an American environmentalist, medical student, thief, and serial killer. Between the ages of 14 and 25 (from 2009 to 2020), Washton murdered a total of fifteen classmates from high school, college, and medical school.
